State is amending Ct. 1 to remove the repeater.  DE has filed a Plea Questionnaire and Waiver of Rights Form with the Court.  Crt reviews plea questionnaire and informs DE of rights. DE pleads Guilty to Ct 1 with the repeater stricken and the subsequent and is stricken.   Crt reviews the police reports   Crt accepts plea, finds factual basis and finds the DE adjudicated guilty of Ct 1 with the repeater stricken and the 2nd and subsequent offense stricken.  Crt orders a PSI and a COMPAS Evaluation be done separate from the PSI.   Court sets out for a SEH.  Court adjourned.  lw  Sentencing hearing scheduled for June 17, 2016 at 03:00 pm.
